Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No distractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.68,0:00:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Reshelving day!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"Understanding Medieval Equestria"\Ngoes in... Pony History.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Modern Spellcasting" â€“\Nthat's Classics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Art of the To-Do List". Actually,\NI kinda wanna read that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This little beauty. It's my\Nbirthday present to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fire ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been aging it for months.\NAnd it's almost ripe!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You took my advice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Just use the whole\Nfloor as one big shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Anypony home? Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a fire ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be at least twenty carats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No inclusions, pristine facets...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And totally delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you guys don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Uh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came by to see if you hadn't\Nany books on historical fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "delicious"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure did! Next week's my birthday.\NAnd this is my birthday dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Start with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the feeling\Nruffled taffeta capes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...are going to make a huge\Ncomeback this season.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to be ahead of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's as tasty\Nas it is beautiful, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything\Nquite so stunning before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh. You really like it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This beautiful gem was\Nmeant to to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.25,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, my little Spikey-wikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the kindest, most\Ngenerous things you've ever done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen Rarity so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never wash this cheek again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just about finished, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything looks perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A wash cloth? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no way, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't gonna wash the cheek\Nthat Rarity kissed and I meant it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over, Spike!\NI'm cleaning that cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Stop it!\N-Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Party time, woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those... for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet they are, birthday boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know you get\Npresents on your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually this is my first\Nbirthday in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually just get one present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,From Twilight. A book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of presents, this is\Nfrom my new line of taffeta capes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make one for each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been inspired by the generosity\Nof my little Spikey-wikey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...who gave me this\Nbeautiful fire ruby...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...one of the kindest acts\NI've ever experienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, I can't thank you\Nenough for this great blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.21,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I really needed a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike. You already\Nthanked me fifteen times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to get a little embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I keep thanking you guys,\Nbut I'm just so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish this party could last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Party can't last forever, cause\Nyou have to go to Sugarcube Corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...cause the Cakes said they have\Na special surprise for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...CAUSE IT'S YOUR BIRTHDAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,NO WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the party can't last forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it doesn't need to end right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. and Mrs. Cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the dragon of the hour!\NHappy birthday, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When we found out\Nit was your birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...we couldn't resist\Ntrying out a new recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! First I get a bunch of great\Npresents from my best friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...and now an amazing sapphire cupcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho ho, what a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! I'm so sorry, Cheerilee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. What's got you so excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie told me I should\Ncome to the Cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...so they could give me a treat,\Ncause it's my birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, happy birthday, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had something to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Everypony should get\Nfun gifts on their birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a great birthday, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish every day was my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie mentions my birthday\Nto the Cakes and I get a cupcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mention it to Cheerilee\Nand I get this great hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Lickety Split! That's\Na pretty cool ball you got there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.41,0:07:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know it's my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This in unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Junebug! It's my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Happy birthday, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna give me something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like a birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I... I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about those\Nflowers? I'll take those.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Junebug.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Spike might have\Ngotten a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You're\Nout here demanding gifts now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. You're right, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what got into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for snapping me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better go give\NCheerilee her hat back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem. See you at home later?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good. Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else has a present for Spikey-wikey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. Little rough night sleep, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the weirdest drea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you!\NWhere'd you get all this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to me, Twilight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know! Think back to last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do after I saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to talk to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to talk to who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I have that globe?\NYou're not using it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're usually not so... grabby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms aren't usually\NTHIS LONG EITHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S HAPPENING TO ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, what theems to be the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Spike...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and something's wrong with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to be half this size.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And he keeps trying to take\Nthings that aren't... his.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.10,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then. Let'th just\Nhave a look-thee, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.75,0:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wittle guy not feewing too good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the brave wittle boy, huh?\NWho's the brave one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What do you think, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think I know\Nwhat the problem is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He is... a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the problem.\NHe's always been a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, that would explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I don't know\Nanything about dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about baby ponies.\NMaybe you should try a vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm flummoxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring me a dog â€“ I've\Ngot it diagnosed in seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Snake even faster. But to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've never seen\Na real-life dragon before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's a good boy? Who's a good boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.35,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He is starting to mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of this fact I am quite sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mature? So he's just... growing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't explain\Nwhy he keeps grabbing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A dragon's heart is prone to greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A steady diet to make growth speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the resulting bigger size\Nonly makes their hunger rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If this trait should go unchecked,\Nif Spike continues to collect...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...more growth will certainly occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He is going to turn into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...the more things the dragon collects,\Nthe bigger and greedier he gets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we stop him before\Nhe's completely out of control?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If his monstrous ways\Nyou wish to impede...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...you must prevent him\Nfrom practicing greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from her, you brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE WANT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting my scooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE WANT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out this amazing broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE WAAANT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, big boy.\NLook at this incredible broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE WANT!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight all you want.\NI'm not letting you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, Spike.\NI just reshelved this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now who in Ponyville\Nwould steal my apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,For that matter, who\Nwould steal my leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike's running wild and\NI need you to lasso him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a good one, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet little Spike running wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, get my rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,HEEELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you...\Nyou tied yourselves up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us out of here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounded like Fluttershy to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy? Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was helping my squirrel friends\Nwith their dance step...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...and all of a sudden a giant\Nrampaging d-d-dragon stormed through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?! But why would Spike\Nsteal my chicken coop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He just pulled it out of the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...and filled it with a bunch\Nof apples and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounded like Pinkie Pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Back! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie Pie! Stop giving him cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving him cake!\NI'm assaulting him with cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you take the cake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's completely out of control.\NWho knows where he'll go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps some more ruffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down, you brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Rarity. We'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Put her down right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If you wouldn't mind, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it, dragon boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be ever so grateful if you'd be\Nso kind as to possibly consider...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop her, scaly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... not some...\Nsort of common... flyswattaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got nothing to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You steal everypony's things,\Nterrorize the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...and use me as a weapon\Nagainst my own friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which as horrible as it is,\NI can almost understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...because you're a dragon and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,BUT THIS...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,THIS IS A CRIME AGAINST FASHION!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! You are not\Ngetting this gemstone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This was given to me\Nby my dear friend Spikey-wikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The kindest, sweetest,\Nmost generous dragon ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is too precious to me to give\Nto a greedy old beast like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Here, Rarity. You take it."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"It would mean even more to see\Nyou happy, than to eat it myself."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.33,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"I... I don't know what to say..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"This is just so generous..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what now? I suppose you'll be\Neating me or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?! You're the rampaging dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Somepony do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, I need to tell you something.\NJust in case we don't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always sort of had a crush...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! I can't believe we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All in a day's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I just have to tell you how\Nabsolutely proud I am of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.42,0:20:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Proud of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was you, who stopped...\Nyou from destroying Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my hero, Spikey-wikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,"Today I learned a great\Nlesson about friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Well, you might think that it would feel\Ngood to get lots and lots of stuff..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"...but it doesn't feel nearly as great\Nas giving something special..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"...to somepony you really care about."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why, I learned that it truly\Nis better to give than to receive..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.11,0:21:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and that kindness and generosity\Nare what lead to true friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"And that's more valuable\Nthan anything in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, almost anything.
